snippet: The board of the insurer WellCare Health Plans fired its chief executive, Alec R. Cunningham, replacing him temporarily with its recently appointed chairman, David J. Gallitano.
abstract: Board of the insurer WellCare Health Plans fires its chief executive Alec R Cunningham, replacing him temporarily with its recently appointed chairman David J Gallitano; also announces its third-quarter earnings jumped 67 percent compared with 2012.
lead_paragraph: The board of the insurer WellCare Health Plans fired its chief executive, Alec R. Cunningham, replacing him temporarily with its recently appointed chairman, David J. Gallitano.

headline.main: Wellcare Fires Its Chief and Announces Soaring Profits
headline.print_headline: WellCare Fires Its Chief and Announces Soaring Profits
